en_611913_0	Brigadier Chanaka Weragoda of Sri Lanka Army General Service Corps (SLAGSC) assumed office as the Director, Directorate of Pay and Records on Tuesday (4) amid religious blessings.
en_611913_1	He succeeded Major General L Wijesundara who retired recently.
en_611913_2	Placing his signature in a formal document, he signified the acceptance of the new office as ‘Seth Pirith’ chanting continued.
en_611913_3	Senior officers, Officers and Other Ranks of the Directorate attended the occasion.
